Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:05.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,At that moment, the wind had suddenly blown.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:08.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Among the scattering cherry blossom petals in full bloom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:14.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,the young masked man murmured something to the cat nestling at his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:22.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Amazingly, the cat had talked as if it was a natural thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:27.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, amazing, the plot's developing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:28.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And then, and then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:31.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And then, the masked man fluttered like...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:36.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're killing the mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.41,0:00:52.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:54.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why the heck is everyone mating?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.85,0:00:56.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I hate spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:05.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I am Ootsuka Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:08.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I am a member of the 4th Foreign Affairs Department in the Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:12.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just between us, I was in the manga club in my university,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:14.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm actually pretty into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:16.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The anime I'm into now, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.33,0:01:18.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Maurice The Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.31,0:01:21.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,My hobby is writing stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:25.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I have done many doujins, and I have a lot of fans as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:32.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The pollen this year is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:34.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I hate spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.81,0:01:41.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,"The masked man standing among the cherry blossom trees."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:46.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This image came to mind from a dream I had last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:49.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No, was it really a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.66,0:01:53.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Even now, it's still a bit vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:02:00.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The members of the 4th unit had decided to hold a flower-watching party that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.91,0:02:02.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:06.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's information that the contractor who was killed was holding onto the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:02:10.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the number for a safety deposit box and we've found out where it is, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:13.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The critical number is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:16.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The stolen goods from the incident at the Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it is related.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:19.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Under a cherry blossom tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:24.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it seems a contractor who had taken some goods from the Gate was buried there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:26.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So, I have to kill that contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:29.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No, your job is only to dig up the goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:32.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's buried is only a sample, but
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:37.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,there should be a numeric password written on a memo or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:38.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:39.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:41.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:44.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that someone may try to steal it ba-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:47.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:49.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:50.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Allergic to pollen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.95,0:02:53.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,During times like this, I'm happy that I'm a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:56.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I hear cats are allergic to pollen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:56.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:00.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Pollen won't affect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:01.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:05.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Contractors don't see dreams and aren't allergic to pollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:07.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first time I heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:10.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, contractors are monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:12.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing strange no matter what it may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:14.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, where's Yin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:16.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That pink girl must've have come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:18.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Pink girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:22.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,From the first time they met when Yin ran away, she's been going there ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:25.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:27.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:27.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:31.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you about an interesting doujin story next time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:33.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's even more risqué!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:36.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's it called? Moe moe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:39.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that she's become involved with a dangerous world now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:40.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her to cut her ties.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:45.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be problematic if she lets out information to a normal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:50.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:51.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Saitou seems a bit gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:01.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's because the chief couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:06.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably dreaming of being alone with her after watching the flowers if things go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:09.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He should just tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.07,0:04:11.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The chief is pretty dense about things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.49,0:04:13.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he has to think about their positions, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:16.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like spring will be coming for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:19.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But there are also people like you who bow down to their colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:23.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,W-What silly things are you saying, Matsumoto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:24.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,H-Here, another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:26.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:31.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Ootsuka, {\i1}he{\i0} just might be the one who's thinking about what'll happen if things go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:35.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be all right, I don't really like young people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:37.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A refined person like you, Matsumoto, is more...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:39.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:46.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,To be truthful...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:49.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't really interested in real men...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:52.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Until that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:55.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:04:57.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be more forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:05:02.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Kouno just disappeared somewhere after some office lady seduced him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, she's a bad drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:08.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you like her, you should tell her clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:11.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you just don't understand a woman's heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:15.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You should research and read some novels!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Novels? {\i1}Those{\i0} things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:18.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, {\i1}those{\i0} things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:21.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand when you write stories, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:23.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Like how delicate people's hearts are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:25.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You write some?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:30.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, oh no, Matsumoto, you're making me embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:34.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you search for MayuMayu on the computer, you can read my stories right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:35.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, are you interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:39.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I may not look like it, but I was once a young man who was into literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:42.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've read quite a bit, like works from Kamizaki and Kajii.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.83,0:05:46.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you really are refined, Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:48.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:52.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Beneath the cherry blossom tree lies a buried corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:54.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Or some mystery like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A buried corpse, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:04.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I shouldn't have asked something that weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.12,0:06:11.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I, feared as the Black Reaper, have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:19.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:24.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What about the numerical password? Is there a memo or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:25.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:32.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is it, it's written right on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:34.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,4697...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,W-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A-A pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:12.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,S-S-Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:18.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is the number.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:23.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,4697635.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:27.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You heard the number just now, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:29.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I-I heard nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:31.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The number 4697635!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:33.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You heard it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's because you said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:37.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:41.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! I can't keep things a secret because of my remuneration!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Remuneration?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:43.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I said something I shouldn't have again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:46.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you go now because you heard things you shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:49.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't remember any numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:51.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Liar! 4697...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,635.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,See? You do remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:57.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's because you said it over and over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:58.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:18.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Things seemed so detached from reality just now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:22.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and all I could remember was the appearance of the person who saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:24.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Especially the line of his collarbone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:33.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered that he had danced like the air, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:36.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And there my memory stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:42.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You got her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:46.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the ones on top to erase her memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:49.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:52.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Public Safety Department?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:54.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Which means she knows that contractors exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:59.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, if we use the ME, it won't mean we've cleared out every trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:05.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If she's part of Public Safety, then at the very least, she won't be stupid and reveal information about us to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:07.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And if she does?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:09.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens, there's only one thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:12.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Take the goods to Huang, Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:15.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:25.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:27.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I could believe it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:35.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But for some reason, my pulsing heart just wouldn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:41.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A story began to flow from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:45.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It was like a drunken spring dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:49.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The cat had told the masked man the mysterious password.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:53.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Number, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:55.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What would work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:06.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And for some reason, this number from my dream was burned onto my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:10.61,Title,,0,0,0,,Episode Twenty-Six Beneath Cherry Blossoms in Full Bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:13.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You lost the goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:15.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:18.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, unexpected things happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:22.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Cats have it tough during this season.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:31.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I desperately looked for it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:33.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll find it for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:37.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You better! Damn it, everyone's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:41.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, don't get too close to that girl, Yin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You know what situation you're in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:47.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Huang, she's made a friend, so a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:49.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:50.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:52.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:00.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:03.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:07.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's mine! I've been looking for this for 2 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:09.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The Maurice pilot is super rare!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:12.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? This Maurice has been waiting for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A book can't possibly wait for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:14.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Your head's gone crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.68,0:11:16.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's crazy is {\i1}your{\i0} head!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:25.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really the MayuMayu who wrote "Maurice's Night?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:26.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:32.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I called such a great person a brute and a swine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:34.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If there were a hole, I'd like to crawl into it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:37.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, you just need to be careful from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:41.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, that story you uploaded yesterday about the masked man was cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:43.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? You read it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:45.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's an original character, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:48.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How is he going to get involved with Maurice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you'll just have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:53.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be unfair to other fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:55.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:59.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But the masked man with delicious collarbones is really great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:00.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I know someone like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:01.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? A masked man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No, someone with nice collarbones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:09.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:18.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Those collarbones...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:20.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,See? They're delicious, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:22.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:24.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:26.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:28.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:32.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the collarbones that saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:35.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:37.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:39.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:41.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:43.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me where he lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:47.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm the only one allowed to stalk him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:51.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've been in a slump these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that really bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:59.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I'd be able to write something interesting if I met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:03.36,Location,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\be1\fs50\an4\fscx81.25\fscy92.5\frx4\fry356\fax-0.35\b0\c&H231E13&\pos(468,421)\frz16.104}Umitsuki Apartments
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:06.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,On that night, my legs had finally made their way to the Umitsuki Apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:11.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,My desire to meet him had overcome me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:28.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ootsuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:33.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ootsuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you so busy that you're losing sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:39.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:41.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just what do I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:45.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:48.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,These feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she looking for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that she knows who we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:03.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You still can't find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:04.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:06.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:09.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you at least remember the password?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I do remember some of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:13.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,4697...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:15.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,4697635.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:18.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say, Yin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:21.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,4697635.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:23.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The password.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:27.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Jun, who had received the password from the masked man,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.69,0:14:31.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,ran full speed to the zoo where Maurice was being kept.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And then he yelled,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:37.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,"Maurice, I need you after all."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:40.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yin, w-what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:42.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Even humans and elephants can love each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:45.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It may be forbidden love,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:48.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,but Maurice, I will live my life with that love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:52.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,"Maurice's Night," this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:54.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:57.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying this number is the complete password?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:15:00.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I just let Kouno go and confir—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:03.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo! It certainly is the right number.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:05.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But, someone else got here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:06.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We were too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that number here, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:12.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but I heard that it's a story she had written.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:13.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Story?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:15.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So you've read it, Matsumoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:18.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The masked man is also written here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:21.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If it's about BK-201...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:24.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ootsuka said that she didn't see him, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:27.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Which means she got information from another source.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:29.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be dangerous if she makes any bad moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:40.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, we've got the goods, but the information has been leaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:43.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They've got you tailed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:45.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You know what to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:47.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:48.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:49.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You lost her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:16.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:23.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:26.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ootsuka! Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here, chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:30.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's a contractor? Do you want to get killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:32.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Contractor? But he's the one who save—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:33.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:51.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:01.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's BK-201, the Black Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:03.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,BK-201?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:04.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You looked for him not knowing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:07.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If I had known, I wouldn't have written the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:10.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You should know he's suspicious because of his mask, at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:12.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:14.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Love is blind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:15.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Love?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:20.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Saitou worries about his position,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:23.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and can't ever confess his love. That just isn't love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:25.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:28.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:33.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's call for reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:36.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They won't make it, take Ootsuka and run, Saitou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:37.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hold him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:39.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.77,0:17:42.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't abandon someone I lov—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:46.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's love! That's all to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:47.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Saitou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.38,0:18:00.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Saitou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:14.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Li-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:18.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:21.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I found it, Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:43.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,W-What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:50.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Strangely, no one remembers what happened that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:54.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems like it wasn't just me who didn't feel clear about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:58.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,the same feeling as if something is stuck in your throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember, chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:05.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I remember saying something really important to you that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:17.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I feel that I found the truth regarding something very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:21.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,However, only one thing was clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:25.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, my allergies have been healed for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:30.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but I feel like I will have a nice spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:32.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Medicine for allergies?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:36.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, seems like it was made by the chemical department from the Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:40.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If everything went well, it could've led to a complete cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:42.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what that fluid was?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:46.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but there's a negative side effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.09,0:19:49.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You lose a few days' worth of memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:53.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's unfortunate, but it'll be a while before it's put to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:58.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Huang, Hei and I haven't lost our memories of that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:03.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because of what Hei said then? That contractors aren't allergic to pollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:07.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? I don't know about contractors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:08.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the pink girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:11.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably heading to Yin's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Huang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:18.72,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We were able to collect the goods thanks to Yin remembering the number.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:20.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:22.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad, Yin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:23.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:33.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:38.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She's not coming today?